Both the Kuripé and the Tepi are beautiful, sacred tools that carry unique medicines of connection. Whether you choose the path of self-reliance with the Kuripé or the path of trust and community with the Tepi, always approach your tools and the medicine with respect, clean intentions, and an open heart.
